OL,5,Ctell schools
OL,7,FSchools have been instructed to
OL,8,Frespond "with caution" to pupil
OL,9,Frequests to socially change gender in
OL,10,Flong-awaited government guidance.
OL,12,FThe guidance says primary school-age
OL,13,Fchildren who are questioning their
OL,14,Fgender could be allowed to use
OL,15,Fdifferent pronouns.
OL,17,FBut it insists schools must always
OL,18,Fcheck with the parents unless there's
OL,19,Fa safeguarding reason not to, and
OL,20,Fconsider any clinical advice families
OL,21,Fhave received.
