OL,7,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,8,Fhas been under pressure from schools
OL,9,Fto publish the guidance, after she
OL,10,Fpromised to "provide clarity" by doing
OL,11,Fso in April last year.
OL,13,FThe guidance cites the "significant
OL,14,Fincrease in the number of children who
OL,15,Fare questioning the way they feel
OL,16,Fabout being a boy or a girl".
OL,18,FIt makes clear it is not schools'
OL,19,Fresponsibility to initiate any
OL,20,Fdiscussions with children about their
OL,21,Fgender identity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
