OL,7,FThe draft guidance, which will be
OL,8,Fconsulted on for ten weeks before
OL,9,Fbecoming legally-binding, also says
OL,10,Fschools must maintain single-sex
OL,11,Fspaces, and there should be no mixed
OL,12,Ftoilets for children over eight years
OL,13,Fold or mixed-sex sleeping arrangements
OL,14,Fon trips.
OL,16,FA child's birth sex must be recorded
OL,17,Fin school and college records.
