OL,7,FThe government insists there should be
OL,8,Fparticular caution on social
OL,9,Ftransitioning with primary school-aged
OL,10,Fchildren, setting out this is expected
OL,11,Fto happen very rarely.
OL,13,FThe new guidance comes after the last
OL,14,FConservative government published
OL,15,Ftheir own guidance in 2023, which told
OL,16,Fschools there is "no general duty" to
OL,17,Fallow children to change their gender
OL,18,Fidentity.
