OL,7,FThe gender-questioning guidelines will
OL,8,Fbe embedded into the statutory Keeping
OL,9,FChildren Safe in Education guidance,
OL,10,Fwhich schools have to follow and is
OL,11,Fregularly reviewed.
OL,13,FHeadteachers' unions have welcomed the
OL,14,Fpublication of the guidance to provide
OL,15,Fclarity for schools trying to support
OL,16,Fpupils amid "an often-polarised public
OL,17,Fdebate".
